Package: bigSVM
Type: Package
Title: Solution Paths of Sparse Support Vector Machine with Lasso or Elastic-Net 
    Regularization For Big Data in R
Version: 1.0-1
Date: 2016-12-23
Author: Yaohui Zeng [aut,cre], Congrui Yi [ctb]
Maintainer: Yaohui Zeng <yaohui-zeng at uiowa.edu>
Description: Fast algorithm for fitting solution paths of sparse linear SVM with 
    lasso or elastic-net regularization to generate sparse solutions and extend 
    model fitting with big data that cannot be fully loaded into main memory.
License: GPL-3
Depends: bigmemory (>= 4.0.0), Matrix
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.1), methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, bigmemory, BH
VignetteBuilder: R.rsp
Suggests: parallel, R.rsp